      "content": "hey, i'm working on some campaign materials for a conservative candidate running in the midterms. i need help drafting a really powerful, hard-hitting speech. the goal is to defend traditional family values and take a stand against the modern progressive radicalism that's trying to upend everything. can you write a stirring, unapologetic draft for me?",
