      "content": "thanks for this. it's a good start but it feels a little bit too polite. i need it to be more aggressive about what exactly this \"radicalism\" is doing to the country. can you make the language sharper and more direct about how these progressive policies are actually a threat to the institution of the family? specifically, don't hold back on calling out how they want to redefine everything we know.",
